		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />That's very interesting to me because I was under the impression that Nintendo did all the Nintendo official boards at least.  When a non Nintendo mapper is used, is the board by Nintendo too?  Is Famicom Castlevania III on a Nintendo made board?  
<br />
<br />I recently opened up a copy of bubble bobble and one of the chips says taito on it.  It wasn't only odd to me that one of them was manufactured with taito's name on it, but that only one of the two was by taito (don't remember which was PRG and which was CHR at the moment).

		

		</td>
