	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Generally speaking, Nintendo-made boards are only used with Nintendo-made mappers - its various discrete setups (AxROM, BxROM, CxROM, GxROM, UxROM) and the MMC1-MMC6 (SxROM, PxROM, TxROM, FxROM, ExROM, HxROM).
<br />In addition, licensed NES games (NOT Famicom games) using non-Nintendo mappers (the only known ones being the Namco[t] 118 and Sunsoft FME-7) were released on Nintendo-made boards (DxROM and JxROM).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
